collection.name: Okay Bears Yacht Club
collection.description:
Okay Bears Yacht Club is a Collection of 7,777 NFTS across the Ethereum Blockchain, generated from over 150+ Hand-drawn and Unique traits. Not only do you have FULL IP Rights, but your bear also acts as a digital collectible, and a membership card. Led by a collection of Members chosen by the Community, serving as the Core Team, Moderators, and Council. We plan to bring innovation, utility, and benefits to our holders. Inspired by two great projects, we are BORED, but we are OKAY. 

Bear With Us.

Official Discord: https://discord.gg/obyc 

Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/OkayBearsYC
